<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-05-06T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-05-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="968" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d968">
                    <head>Mutual Aid Society of Neuveville</head>
                    <note rend="inline" rendition="#center" type="source">[Translation.]</note>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Neuveville</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-05-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 6, 1865</date>.</dateline>
                    <p rend="center">
                        <hi rend="italic">Concurrence of the Mutual Aid Society of Neuveville,
                            canton of Berne, in the address of sympathy and condolence to the
                            American Union by the Swiss people</hi>.</p>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The Mutual Aid Society met to-day and decided
                        to join in the spontaneous manifestation of the Swiss people, and thank the
                        citizens who proposed it.</p>
                    <p>It also requested its officers to sign the present resolution of concurrence
                        and send it to its address, in the name of the society.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <list>
                                <item>H. TSCHIFFE, <hi rend="italic">President</hi>.</item>
                                <item>FRED IMER, <hi rend="italic">Vice-President</hi>.</item>
                                <item>SCHEM KARLEN, <hi rend="italic">Cashier</hi>.</item>
                                <item>E. CIBOLLET, <hi rend="italic">Secretary</hi>.</item>
                            </list>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>